@startuml

start

:1. Mapping Engine sends transformed data;

:2. Receive data batch;

:3. Determine Target Format from Profile;

if (E3: Invalid Target Format?) then (Yes)

    :Issue warning;

    :Use default strategy;

endif

:4. Select appropriate\nOutputWriter strategy;

:5. Apply File Naming Pattern;

:6. Generate content\n(Header + Rows);

:7. Write file to\noutput directory;

if (E1: Write File Failed?) then (Yes)

    :Push entire batch to DLQ;

    :Notify operator;

    stop

endif

:8. Validate file\n(format, row count);

if (E2: Format Validation Failed?) then (Yes)

    :Log detailed error;

    :Push batch to DLQ;

    stop

endif

:9. Write Audit Log;

:Update status;

stop

@enduml